Initial set of user stories at the Initiative and Epic level.

Epic: As a user, I want to be able to easily find and navigate the restaurant's website.

User Story: As a user, I want to be able to find the restaurant's website easily by searching for it in a search engine.

User Story: As a user, I want to be able to access the restaurant's website from a variety of devices, including desktop computers, laptops, tablets, and smartphones.

User Story: As a user, I want to be able to easily find the information I need on the restaurant's website, such as the menu, contact information, and hours of operation.

Epic: As a user, I want to be able to learn about the restaurant's authentic Indian cuisine and ambiance.

User Story: As a user, I want to be able to see photos of the restaurant's food and ambiance on the website.

User Story: As a user, I want to be able to read about the restaurant's history and the chefs' culinary expertise.

User Story: As a user, I want to be able to learn about the different types of Indian cuisine and the ingredients that are used.

Epic: As a user, I want to be able to make a reservation online.

User Story: As a user, I want to be able to see a real-time availability of tables on the website.

User Story: As a user, I want to be able to enter my party size and preferred date and time for a reservation.
User Story: As a user, I want to receive a confirmation email once my reservation has been made.

Epic: As a user, I want to be able to order food online for pickup or delivery.

User Story: As a user, I want to be able to view the restaurant's menu online and add items to my cart.
User Story: As a user, I want to be able to enter my contact information and delivery address for online orders.

User Story: As a user, I want to be able to pay for my online order securely through a credit card or online payment system.

Epic: As a user, I want to be able to stay up-to-date on the latest news and events at the restaurant.

User Story: As a user, I want to be able to sign up for the restaurant's email newsletter to receive updates on new menu items, special offers, and upcoming events.

User Story: As a user, I want to be able to follow the restaurant on social media to see photos, videos, and announcements.

User Story: As a user, I want to be able to leave reviews of the restaurant online to share my experiences with other potential customers.
